{Speech 2}{}{You fought gloriously.@@I watched the course of the battle. It was... Magnificent.@@Next time I'll bet my daily ration on you.@@I hope we'll see you again at the Trial.@@The replicators don't work in vain, your team has proven it once again.@@You're a true fighter. May the right hand of the Hub touch you.}
